SIGODLIWE isinqumo mayelana nesicelo sikahulumeni sokudlulisa isinqumo esakhishwa yinkantolo eyathi imithetho kathaqa yesigaba sesine nesesihlanu ayihambisani nomthethosisekelo wakulel Inkantolo enkulu yaseGauteng iyona obekulalelwe kuyo lesi sicelo. UMnyango wezokuBusa ngokuBambisana nezoMdabu wanikwa ithuba lokuthi iyibuyekeze le mithetho. UJaji Norman Davis wacelwa wu-Advocate Wim Trengove SC, owayemele uNgqongqoshe walo Mnyango uDkt Nkosazane Dlamini-Zuma ukuthi anike lo Mnyango ithuba  lokusidlulisela kwenye inkantolo  lesi sinqumo ukuze sibuyekezwe. UTrengove wathi maningi kakhulu amathuba okuthi enye inkantolo ibone ngenye indlela. Umhlali wasePretoria uReyno de Beer nenhlangano yakhe iLiberty Fighters Network, ekuqaleni kwale nyanga yababela enkantolo ifuna imithetho kathaqa ithathwe njengaleyo engawakhi umqondo futhi engahambisani nomthethosisekelo. UDkt Dlamini Zuma wathi imigomo nemithetho kathaqa yayenzelwe ukulekelela abantu bakuleli ukuthi bavikeleke kwiCovid-19. 